[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     11[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     12[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## What Was Reconstructed
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     13[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     14[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A minimal Maven project (`repro/`) with a single JUnit test that simulates the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     15[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Tomcat redeploy scenario using two sequential `URLClassLoader` instances in the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     16[0m:[38;5;10m[49m same JVM. The test exercises the exact code path from the original stack trace:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     17[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     18[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
