[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    109[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    110[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## Assumptions and Caveats
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    111[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    112[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 1. **Java version dependency.** The `LinkageError` is a Java 8 JVM behavior. Java 11+
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    113[0m:[38;5;10m[49m    changed how loader constraints are tracked for `MethodHandle` invocations, eliminating
