[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    120[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    121[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 3. **No Spring required.** Spring's role in the original was only to manage the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    122[0m:[38;5;10m[49m    Lucene bean lifecycle. The `LinkageError` occurs in Lucene's `AttributeFactory`
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    123[0m:[38;5;10m[49m    regardless of Spring. The test exercises the Lucene code path directly.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    124[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
